definition: to get rid of/to remove/to exclude/to eliminate/to wipe out/to divide/except/not including

to fall/to drop/to lag behind/to lose/to go missing/to reduce/fall (in prices)/to lose (value, weight etc)/to wag/to swing/to turn/to change/to exchange/to swap/to show off/to shed (hair)/(used after certain verbs to express completion, fulfillment, removal etc)

sentences.english: The motion that the remark of the last speaker be expunged from the record.
sentences.chinese: 該提議要求把最後一個發言的人的講話從記錄上除掉。

sentences.english: The motion that the remark of the last speaker (should) be expunged from the record.
sentences.chinese: 該提議要求把最後一個發言的人的講話從記錄上除掉。

sentences.english: It also wipes out the system restore with a reset, making it harder to recover the system.
sentences.chinese: 它還清除掉系統還原設置，使其難以恢復系統。

sentences.english: So he constantly removed distractions and demands on the conscious mind.
sentences.chinese: 因此，他不斷地移除掉意識心理上的干擾和要求。

sentences.english: Village work to get to meet with siew, he put away the resolution dove.
sentences.chinese: 中村功得以脫身去與蕭船見面，他決議除掉白鴿。

sentences.english: In that day the Lord will snatch away their finery: the bangles and headbands and crescent necklaces
sentences.chinese: 到那日，主必除掉她們華美的腳釧，髮網，月牙圈。

sentences.english: And Nathan said unto David, The LORD also hath put away thy sin; thou shalt not die.
sentences.chinese: 拿單說，耶和華已經除掉你的罪，你必不至於死。

sentences.english: The student whited out those letters at the edge of the page.
sentences.chinese: 那個學生把那頁邊上的字母除掉。

sentences.english: I used weedkiller to get rid of the weeds in the garden.
sentences.chinese: 我用殺蟲劑來除掉花園裏的蟲子。

sentences.english: Oppressed and condemned, he was taken away, and who would have thought any more of his destiny?
sentences.chinese: 他受了不義的審判而被除掉，有誰懷念他的命運？

sentences.english: Circumcise therefore the foreskin of your heart, and be no longer stubborn.
sentences.chinese: 所以你們要將心裏的污穢除掉，不可再硬著頸項。

sentences.english: Turk action qol at quite remove kato action failure.
sentences.chinese: 特科行動組組善於挺除掉加藤的行動失敗。

sentences.english: The Bible should be demythologized and examined for its historical value.
sentences.chinese: 應該除掉聖經的神話色彩，審視聖經的歷史價值。

sentences.english: The cashew nuts contain a toxin which is eliminated through frying.
sentences.chinese: 腰果堅果含有毒素，油炸後便會除掉。

sentences.english: Today, I got fed up with the amount of hair on my feet, so I went to get my foot hair waxed off.
sentences.chinese: 今天，我厭煩了腳上厚厚的汗毛，便去把它用蠟除掉。

sentences.english: The second hexane wash may be decanted off and the wet solid screened.
sentences.chinese: 第二次的乙烷洗液可以除掉，溼的固體進行過篩。
